en Gemengelage, fragt nach der Rolle von Religion und Nation im Umgang mit dem Tod, diskutiert das Verhältnis von Körper und Emotionen und erkundet, wie Trauer sich räumlich entfaltete.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-NC-ND 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0 uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2022) 0aDeathxSocial aspectszItalyxHistoryy19th century. 0aFuneral rites and ceremonieszItalyxHistoryy19th century. 0aMourning customszItalyxHistoryy19th century. 4aItalien. 4aKulturgeschichte. 4aTod. 4aTrauer. 7aHISTORY / Europe / Germany.2bisacsh  aCultural History.  aDeath.  aEmotions.  aItaly.  aMourning.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2018 Part 1z978311076248808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2018z978311071955008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018z9783110603255oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2018z9783110603149oZDB-23-DEG0 cEPUBz97831105943620 cprintz978311059565940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783110598513zOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110598513zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110598513/original  a978-3-11-071955-0 DG Plus eBook-Package 2018b2018  a978-3-11-076248-8 DG Plus DeG Package 2018 Part 1b2018  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DEGb2018  aZDB-23-DGGb2017  aZDB-23-GOA